Description: Anti-detection browser automation tool
 Antidetect Browser provides stealth browser automation with anti-detection
 capabilities. It includes fingerprint spoofing, proxy management, and
 profile management features.
 .
 Features:
  - Browser fingerprint spoofing
  - Profile management with isolation
  - Proxy support (HTTP, SOCKS5)
  - Camoufox-based stealth automation
  - PyQt6 GUI for easy management
  - Redis-based session management
 .
 This package installs the application to /opt/antidetect-browser and
 provides desktop integration.
